{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"You know how best to hide. You gain the following benefits:\n\n- Increase your Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20.\n\n- You gain proficiency in the Stealth skill. If you are already proficient in the skill, you add double your proficiency bonus to checks you make with it.\n\n- If you are hidden, you can move up to 10 feet in the open without revealing yourself if you end the move in a position where you're not clearly visible","level":1}],"isFeature":false,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Stealthy","notes":"","type":"Feat"}